REM *    Checkbox "Use Output Window".
REM *
REM * 5. Call 'External Tool' in Atmel Studio 6.
REM *    Tools -> BossacArduinoDue(Debug) for Debug Build
REM *    Tools -> BossacArduinoDue(Release) for Release Build
